OL,7,FThe UK is to launch a national
OL,8,Fclinical trial of a "poo transplant"
OL,9,Fthat researchers believe could treat
OL,10,Fadvanced liver disease and fight
OL,11,Fantimicrobial resistance.
OL,13,FIt follows the success of an initial
OL,14,Ftrial where patients were given a
OL,15,Ffaecal transplant via an endoscopy,
OL,16,Fwhere a tube is inserted into the
OL,17,Fbody, proving that the process can
OL,18,Fdramatically improve gut health.
OL,3,CHow a 'poo transplant' trial could
OL,4,Ctransform care for liver disease
